<i>noun</i>: 보상 [보ː상], 변상 [변ː상] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>보상 [보ː상]</dt><br>
<dd>compensation; indemnification</dd><br>
<dd>발생한 손실이나 손해를 갚음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making up for losses or damages that have been occurred.</dd><br>
<dt>변상 [변ː상]</dt><br>
<dd>1. paying back; reimbursement</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 빌린 돈을 갚음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of paying back borrowed money.</dd><br>
<dd>2. compensation</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 입힌 손해를 돈으로 갚거나 원래의 상태로 되돌려 줌.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of paying someone money for inflicting damage, or restoring something to its former state.</dd><br>
<dd>3. indemnification</dd><br>
<dd>죄를 지은 대가로 돈이나 값이 나가는 물건을 냄.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of paying money or an expensive item for doing something wrong.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>